    • getDomainResultResultJavaType

      public Class<T> getDomainResultResultJavaType()
      Description copied from interface: RowReader
      The type actually returned from this reader's RowReader.readRow(org.hibernate.sql.results.jdbc.spi.RowProcessingState) call, accounting for any transformers.

      May be null to indicate that no transformation is applied.

      Ultimately intended for use in comparing values that are being de-duplicated
